OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged assault in Ebbw Vale
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a 37-year-old died
OL,8,Ffollowing an incident outside a pub in
OL,9,FBlaenau Gwent.
OL,11,FGwent Police said the victim, a man
OL,12,Ffrom Tredegar, who had been in a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening condition following
OL,14,Freports of an assault in Ebbw Vale on
OL,15,FFriday, 20 February, had died.
OL,17,FOfficers were called to The Picture
OL,18,FHouse in Bethcar Street after 11.30pm
OL,19,Fon Friday.
