OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged assault in Ebbw Vale
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man from Cardiff was
OL,7,Farrested in connection with the
OL,8,Fincident and remains in custody,
OL,9,Fpolice confirmed on Tuesday, 24
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FPolice said enquiries were ongoing and
OL,13,Fanyone with information is asked to
OL,14,Fcall 101, quoting incident number
OL,15,F2600055384.
